<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Trump&#8217;s Business Interests Are Shaping His Response to the Coronavirus</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="909" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-1200x909.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="Donald Trump sits in a chair with his arms crossed and yells" itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-1200x909.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-400x303.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-200x152.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-800x606.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-1536x1164.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-2048x1552.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-2400x1818.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="909" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="Donald Trump sits in a chair with his arms crossed and yells" itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-1200x909.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-400x303.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-200x152.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-800x606.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-1536x1164.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-2048x1552.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0311-trump-sitting-2400x1818.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020