<article class="row hentry post-268981 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-coronavirus tag-donald-trump tag-real-estate tag-trump-hotels section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
