<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/trump-bears-full-responsibility-for-botched-response-to-coronavirus-in-us/" title="Trump Bears Full Responsibility for Botched Response to Coronavirus in US">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0309-trump-corona-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Donald Trump stands inside of a laboratory wearing a red maga hat" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0309-trump-corona-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0309-trump-corona-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0309-trump-corona-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0309-trump-corona-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0309-trump-corona-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
